main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 2041/75 is hereby amended as follows:
(a) the following expressions are added to the first paragraph of Article 2a:
'Eisagogí chýdin í se ámeses syskevasíes anóteres ton 5 lítron ',
'Eisagogí se ámeses syskevasíes anóteres í íses pros 5 lítra ';
(b) the following expression is added to the second subparagraph of Article 9 (2):
'Chorís epistrofí se chríma';
(c) the following expression is added to the fourth subparagraph of Article 9 (3):
'Chorís eisforá';
(d) the following expression is added to Article 12 (1):
'I posótis anaféretai stin poiótita týpoy'.
